original: Another uneventful day: holding the gates, doing repeats, not napping… The Mistress called you, very unusual for her to be awake at daytime.  She asked to lock down everything and go track the head maid for "security reasons".  You complied, almost caught up, really just at the boundary of your vision, when she… vanished?  Seems that you lost yourself too, you can't recall the last time humans walked without qi.
translation: 又是平淡无奇的一日：看门、重复传话、不能打瞌睡…大小姐在叫你过去了，对大小姐来说在白天还醒着是很不寻常的。出于“安全考虑”，她让你把所有东西都锁好，然后找女仆长领班。你照做了，就差一点就赶上了，但她出现在视线边缘时，她就那样…消失了？随后你也迷失了自我，现在你已经想不起来，上一次人类没有气还能走是什么时候了。

original: Fighting in Heaven is a bit different than normal: one can go all in since there's no damage to recover from.  This variation of that style is simplifying that by focusing on excessive force with very, if any, proper defensive maneuvers.  Not that you needed them before anyways.
translation: 在天界里战斗有点不同于平常：一个人可以全力以赴地战斗，因为没有伤害需要恢复。这种风格的变化是通过专注于过度的力量，很少，如果有的话，有适当的防御动作来简化这一点。不过你之前也不需要它们。

original: It was yet another uneventful day down there helping Okuu with the reactor: corpses burning, spirits floating, fusion fuel being distilled, eating lunch with your master… You craved a nap at the Shrine, so you snuck to reach your goal… and somehow got lost.  You smell death *everywhere*, which would be amazing if it wasn't that these dead are moving, they're angry, and they're not listening to what you have to say.
translation: 又是在无聊的地方度过的一天，帮助灵乌路空维护反应炉：烧尸体、怨灵漂浮、提炼聚变燃料、和你的主人一起吃午饭……你想在神社里小睡一会儿，于是偷偷摸摸地去了那里……结果迷路了，你闻到四处都是死亡的气息，如果不是这些尸体还在动、很生气的，还没法和你交流，那就更棒了。

original: Resuming your duties after lunch, you master asked you to go look for Orin, and she was indeed missing again.  You went to the surface, noticing the friendly cave spider wasn't at her usual spot, maybe both went together!  You know she likes to go nap at the Shrine, so you went… to the wrong one, and noticing this was no mountain, nothing close, you looked back, you saw no "back".  You're aware you can get lost sometimes, but this is too much even for yourself.  Now you have to find Orin, find the Tsuchigumo, and return.
translation: 吃午饭后你开始了工作，主人让你去找橙，果然她又失踪了。你去了地面，发现友好的洞穴蜘蛛不在平时的位置，也许她们两人一起走了！你知道她喜欢在神社打盹，于是你去了…错的那一条路。你发现这里没有山，什么也没有。你回过头，发现找不到归路。你知道自己有时会迷路，但这对你来说太离谱了。现在你必须找到橙和土蜘蛛，然后回家。

original: Resuming your duties after lunch, you master asked you to go look for Orin, and she was indeed missing again.  You went to the surface, noticing the friendly cave spider wasn't at her usual spot, maybe both went together!  You know she likes to go nap at the Shrine, so you went… to the wrong one, and noticing this was no mountain, nothing close.  Looking back, you saw no "back".  You're aware you can get lost sometimes, but this is too much even for yourself.  Now you have to find Orin, find the Tsuchigumo, and return.
translation: Resuming your duties after lunch, you master asked you to go look for Orin, and she was indeed missing again.  You went to the surface, noticing the friendly cave spider wasn't at her usual spot, maybe both went together!  You know she likes to go nap at the Shrine, so you went… to the wrong one, and noticing this was no mountain, nothing close.  Looking back, you saw no "back".
